{"tid":2216823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭稱「不吐不快」：警方怎會打壓新聞自由或篩選記者呢？","createTime":"2020-09-25T03:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T04:58:07.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79adc6446b3c9d038a17af3b04a848b55fc63146","tid":2216823,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"警方日前修改《警察通例》，將傳媒代表定義修訂為已在政府新聞處新聞發布系統（GNMIS）登記的傳媒機構，行政長官林鄭月娥凌晨發帖支持警方，指這是警隊的特別安排，並非打壓新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭在帖文開首已說看到新聞持續圍繞「傳媒代表」定義一事，令她「有點不吐不快」。她說 GNMIS 是一個客觀、開放、一視同仁的服務平台，警方以此來界定誰是「傳媒代表」，為傳媒「在警隊行動中提供特別安排，例如可進入封鎖區內採訪，可在特別位置攝影」，「又怎會是打壓新聞自由或篩選記者呢？」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭指，幾年前有被 GNMIS 拒之門外的純網媒 (online-only media) 曾作出投訴，她自己於就任行政長官後，在 2017 年 9 月把 GNMIS 向純網媒開放，過去三年，超過 30 間純網媒機構獲得登記。她強調，《基本法》保障香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版等的自由，是不會改變的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%80%8E%E6%9C%83%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%88%96%E7%AF%A9%E9%81%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%91%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2e_OuvXJM5dFGSP4ZUwVJtBYworScRnY49X55zt2mI8kq1UEgHExTWF9Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25AB-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25AF%25A9%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2591%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2e_OuvXJM5dFGSP4ZUwVJtBYworScRnY49X55zt2mI8kq1UEgHExTWF9Q&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=1981875b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E7%25A8%25B1-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%2590%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25AB-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2580%258E%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%25AF%25A9%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2591%25A2%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2e_OuvXJM5dFGSP4ZUwVJtBYworScRnY49X55zt2mI8kq1UEgHExTWF9Q&h=772a4f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1-%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%90%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%80%8E%E6%9C%83%E6%89%93%E5%A3%93%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E6%88%96%E7%AF%A9%E9%81%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%91%A2/?fbclid=IwAR2e_OuvXJM5dFGSP4ZUwVJtBYworScRnY49X55zt2mI8kq1UEgHExTWF9Q</a>"},{"pid":"b64f14c6e99b3b4257e8a9845a881cda30460c5f","tid":2216823,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:56:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9409181ed198f4447172fa9539aa8b8f0adccd88","tid":2216823,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daff58e389df4038a1e968524d17eff204f13497","tid":2216823,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥：警方界定「傳媒代表」定義非打壓新聞<br />\n<br />\n警方修改《警察通例》下「傳媒代表」定義，行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站表示，警方採用的是政府新聞處GNMIS的傳媒機構名單，是一個客觀、開放、一視同仁的服務平台，以界定誰是「傳媒代表」，為他們在警隊行動中提供特別安排，例如可進入封鎖區內採訪，可在特別位置攝影，一如獲安排出席記者招待會或出席活動做採訪，反問怎可能是打壓新聞自由或篩選記者。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又強調，《基本法》保障香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版等的自由，是不會改變。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2358828&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b3b35f80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2358828</a>"},{"pid":"e9beb721241d349863b78bcfa7a83e10759c20d5","tid":2216823,"uid":50021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T04:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc57795f91e76d0f41311